title: An Act relative to electronic security for the Commonwealth

abstracts.abstract: By Representative Vaughn of Wrentham, a petition (accompanied by bill, House, No. 105) of Marcus S. Vaughn relative to electronic security for certain procurements involving electronic or cyber security equipment components.  Advanced Information Technology, the Internet and Cybersecurity.
